SJMP LOOP

END


✅ 11. PIR Sensor
ORG 0000H

LOOP: JB P1.0, ON
CLR P2.0
SJMP LOOP

ON: SETB P2.0
SJMP LOOP

END

✅ 12. Ultrasonic
ORG 0000H

LOOP: JB P1.1, DETECT
CLR P2.0
SJMP LOOP

DETECT: SETB P2.0
SJMP LOOP

END


